ingredient adds a deep, umami rich flavour to anything it touches - one taste and we know you’ll be hooked. Here, you’ll make a smokey
and salty glaze that transforms eggplant into a caramelised and roasted delight. With fragrant garlic rice and flavourful greens, this is a vegetarian feast in a bowl.

